title: Prominent Baltimore activist Deray McKesson meets with Hillary Clinton about police reform
text: Prominent activist Deray McKesson met with leading Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton Friday to push for police reform. McKesson, a Baltimore native and former public school administrator here, is part of a team called Campaign Zero, which seeks to end police killings in America.... ...
